snippet.title: Fear & Hunger 2: Termina - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Finally, after 3+ years of development, the game is available on Steam. More platforms will follow once I've gotten a good night's sleep.

Deepest apologies for any potential jank and issues. The work on the game is far from over, but I feel it is at a point where I can open the flood gates.

It's a weird game. Very curious in hearing what you think of it.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2171440/Fear__Hunger_2_Termina/
